# ImgBB API key for the submit-dialog thumbnail upload.
# Get a free key at https://api.imgbb.com (signup) → "About" → API key.
# This key is bundled into the client JS (VITE_ prefix). ImgBB's free-tier
# keys are designed to be public, but keep this on the free tier — a paid-tier
# key exposed here could have its quota abused by third parties.
VITE_IMGBB_KEY=
